_sText: This is a remake of gg_fy_killfast  I had to add lights, because the first version is in full bright, these screens look kinda dark but the map i feel has perfect lighting for the style so have fun, and I hope those who didnt like the first will like this version with the lights :) and i will admit it looks smoother now. thnaks to my critics. as always please voice an opinion if you can.. thank you.
